org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.profile.Codegen

Interface GeneratorHint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratorHintImpl

    public interface GeneratorHint
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Generator Hint'. Information about the generator that should be used.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Element
    • Language
    • Generator ID
    See Also:
    CodegenPackage.getGeneratorHint()
